      • Treasure

        public Treasure(java.lang.String nameOfTreasure,
                java.lang.String image,
                int scoreGranted,
                int positionX,
                int positionY,
                java.lang.String imageInAscii)
        name:Treasure
        Treasure builder
        pre: Treasure data must be different from null
        post: an object of type Treasure will be created
        Parameters:
        nameOfTreasure - String is the name of the treasure
        image - String is the URL of the treasure image
        scoreGranted - int is the number of points awarded for finding the treasure
        positionX - int is the position on the x-axis of the treasure in the level
        positionY - int is the position on the y-axis of the treasure in the level
        imageInAscii - String is the randomly generated image that corresponds to the treasure
